## Gerald Gicharu's Portfolio

Welcome to Gerald Gicharu's portfolio website! This site showcases my work as a Full-Stack Web Developer and Network Technician, featuring information about my skills, projects, and how to get in touch.

# Live Site
You can view the live portfolio at: https://geraldggportfolio.netlify.app

# Features
 * About Me: Learn more about Gerald's background, education, and experience.
 * Skills: Detailed list of technical skills including Networking, Frontend and Backend Development, and Problem-Solving.
 * Portfolio: Highlights of recent projects with descriptions and images.
 * Contacts: Contact form and social media links to get in touch with Gerald.

# Technologies Used
 * HTML
 * CSS
 * JavaScript
 * React
 * Python (Flask & Django)
 * MySQL

# Installation
To run this project locally, clone the repository and open the index.html file in your preferred browser.


    git clone git@github.com:Gerald-GG/New-Portfolio.git

    cd New-Portfolio

 * Open index.html in your web browser.

# Usage
Feel free to browse through the different sections to get a sense of my work and skills. If you have any questions or would like to connect, use the contact form or reach out via the social media links provided.

# Contribution
If you would like to contribute to this project, please follow these steps:

 1. Fork the repository.
 2. Create a new branch (git checkout -b feature-branch).
 3. Make your changes.
 4. Commit your changes (git commit -am 'Add new feature').
 5. Push to the branch (git push origin feature-branch).
 6. Create a new Pull Request.

